# Medical Documents Directory
# ==========================
# Place your medical knowledge documents here for RAG ingestion.
#
# Supported formats:
# - .txt (plain text)
# - .md (markdown)
# - .json (structured data)
# - .pdf (PDF documents)
#
# Recommended organization:
# documents/
# ├── glioma/
# │   ├── overview.md
# │   ├── imaging_features.txt
# │   └── treatment_overview.txt
# ├── meningioma/
# ├── pituitary_tumor/
# ├── brain_metastases/
# ├── alzheimer/
# └── general_neurology/
#
# Run ingestion with:
# python main.py ingest --path ./rag/knowledge_base/documents

